{"tid":1966369,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］點先可以令藍絲知道抗爭對長遠經濟有利","createTime":"2020-04-10T06:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T06:50:59.000Z","uid":310637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"166c650b1f6e7fb7765a567f80e6542340ff8bac","tid":1966369,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲成日捉住我地搞到啲經濟差曬嚟講<br />\n但其實經濟衰退好大原因係中美貿易戰拖累<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國一直吸緊香港血，等深圳上海發展完，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港將會毫無利益價值</strong></span></span>，對中國冇威脅<br />\n<br />\n至於究竟中國點吸香港血呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大灣區計畫加強深港兩地合作，為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">未來經濟中心由香港轉移去深圳</span></strong></span>做準備<br />\n<br />\n一系列大白象工程消耗香港庫房，本土福利就唔改善，不斷送錢俾大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民退保講咗咁耐都唔推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1000億</strong></span></span><br />\n東江水統包制<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">50億每年</span></span></strong><br />\n高鐵深圳灣口岸<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">43億</span></span></strong><br />\n沙中線<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">900億</span></strong></span><br />\n機場跑道<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1415億(至少)</span></span></strong><br />\n明日大嶼<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>10000億</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(預計，未知超支幾多)<br />\n<br />\n上面數字我唔肯定啱晒<br />\n但肯定仲有好多數唔哂嘅豪華工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府亂鳩咁洗錢都算，仲打算剝奪香港人自由<br />\n如果唔出嚟抗爭，遲早俾政府用撚曬啲錢<br />\n所以藍絲係咪仲咁天真以為撐政府可以令經濟變好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">同你講長遠嚟講香港只會不斷洗錢送撚曬啲錢上中國，然後香港毫無利益價值，中共可以毫無顧忌咁打壓香港，然後就冇然後了...</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔好話冇可能就唔叫，機會真係嚟到嘅時候你捉都捉唔住</strong></span>"},{"pid":"39a6cabe0c2b2d032a44334abbaf12cb3a1bfe09","tid":1966369,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:50:59.000Z","msg":"佢地自顧短期利益<br />\n邊面有著數就會跟邊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大中華情意結除外"}]}